671
00:55:12,290 --> 00:55:15,410
Anong variable.

672
00:55:15,410 --> 00:55:18,580
Magwala ka! Naliligaw ang lahat!

673
00:55:18,580 --> 00:55:24,120
Simula ngayon, nasa emergency na tayo! Alamin na walang pera na gagastusin!

674
00:55:27,420 --> 00:55:30,920
